kitty-launcher Manual
*********************

This manual describes kitty-launcher version 0.2.0.

kitty-launcher is a robust Rust wrapper for the kitty terminal emulator that
allows launching terminal sessions with flexible configuration presets. It
provides a convenient way to start preconfigured terminal environments with
custom layouts, working directories, and applications.

