Session Names
*************

Session Name Validation
=======================

Session names must follow these rules:

  • Must not be empty
  • Can contain alphanumeric characters, hyphens (-), underscores (_), and dots (.)
  • Cannot contain path separators (/ or \)
  • Cannot be special directory names (. or ..)
  • Cannot contain special characters

Valid Examples
==============

   dev
   work-session
   project_v1
   dev.backup
   z-tools.session

Invalid Examples
================

   ../evil           (path traversal attempt)
   /root             (absolute path)
   dev/session       (contains path separator)
   dev@home          (contains invalid character)
   .                 (special directory)


