Examples
********

Launch a Session
================

   kitty-launcher dev

Searches for and launches the dev session (or dev.session).


Launch with Explicit Extension
===============================

   kitty-launcher dev.session

Launches the dev.session file directly.


Create a New Session
====================

   kitty-launcher --create my-project

Creates a new session file at:
   ~/.local/etc/kitty/my-project.session


Display Help
============

   kitty-launcher --help
   kitty-launcher -h

Shows comprehensive help message with all options and examples.


Display Version
===============

   kitty-launcher --version
   kitty-launcher -V

Shows version information and licensing details.


