Exit Codes
**********

Exit Code 0
===========

Successful execution. Either:
  • A session was launched successfully
  • A new session file was created successfully


Exit Code 1
===========

Runtime error. Examples:
  • kitty terminal not found in PATH
  • Failed to spawn kitty process
  • Failed to set environment variables


Exit Code 2
===========

Configuration error. Examples:
  • Session name failed validation
  • Configuration file not found
  • Invalid arguments provided


